[thinking] **Considering serialization requirements**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I'm trying to figure out if ObjectDataType can write an array of ComponentValue using elementType.write for each ComponentValue. I wonder if ComponentValue records need to be serializable; specifically, they only become serializable if they implement Serializable. If not, ObjectDataType defaults to serializing through ObjectOutputStream, and that could fail if it's not serializable. So, I think ComponentValue must implement Serializable, and records can do that too.
